Speaker 2: Does that mean in the mailbox tomorrow, or are you guys shipping it out tomorrow?

Speaker 1: No, Mr. Lanningham, that was me actually, so it'll be arriving tomorrow at your mailbox.

Speaker 2: Ah, very nice.

Speaker 1: Yeah, at the PO box. You'll see it there.

Speaker 2: Awesome. Thank you, man.

Speaker 1: No problem. Thank you. Bye-bye now.

Speaker 2: Thank you.
